    <criterion>Decision points rewritten — "which executor type?" replaces "which ActionType?"</criterion>
    <criterion>At least 3 worked examples present (AiCompletion + Condition + AiAnalysis)</criterion>
    <criterion>WHY paragraph added explaining R7 dispatch unification</criterion>
    <criterion>Cross-references to spec FR-07, FR-12, FR-30, CLAUDE.md §10, constraint §G present</criterion>
    <criterion>No SUPERSEDED markers (NFR-08)</criterion>
